snippet.title: Jiten Civil Engineering Academy 5M
snippet.description:
Educational Channel for Civil Engineering Govt Jobs Aspirants, 2021. 

Here you will find the basic Civil Engineering  and General Studies Knowledge which will be the foundation to clear your Civil Engineering Exam. 

I , myself have cleared two Govt written Exam of APSC, PWD 3f and AE PNRD-2021 Recently and have attempted APSC Technical VIVA thrice. 
So, every Questions and answer given here, will be based on my vast experience of studying and preparation of my own Exam.

Thank you, Hope it can help you all in any way possible for your Exam-2021
